{"tid":1888404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會口罩用懲教署供應商 唯一分別是由CSI改為工聯會標誌","createTime":"2020-02-20T07:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T10:17:48.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ec36334bb0bc18235f82490817c892f127b73195","tid":1888404,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎襲港，掀起口罩搶購潮。工聯會借用永富容器在大埔工業邨的廠房，開設本地口罩工場，預料首階段可月產10萬個口罩，目前已送往檢驗認證，需要10至14日才可正式流出市面。這批口罩的原材料供應商與懲教署一樣，但會由CSI改為工聯會的標誌。<br />\n<br />\n口罩工場目前籌得的500萬元，包括保險界立法會議員陳健波擔任行政總裁的立橋保險集團捐出100萬元，香港廣東社團總會主席龔俊龍捐出100萬元，工銀亞洲捐出100萬元，張廣軍捐出100萬元，青海嘉潤捐出60萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27098/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E6%9C%83-%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E7%BD%B2-27098/%E3%80%90csi%E8%AE%8A%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E6%A8%99%E8%AA%8C%E3%80%91%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%AD%E5%BB%A0%E6%9C%88%E7%94%A210%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86%E8%88%87%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A3-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F27098%2F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%25BC%25BA-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25BD%25B2-27098%2F%25E3%2580%2590csi%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25AA%258C%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%2594%25A210%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%259D%2590%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A8%25A3-&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=ff7644a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27098/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E